Package: plotr
Title:  Plot Themes for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Miu Shing", family = "Hung", email = "matthewhungms@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0004-0412-4374"))
Description: Provides elegant themes and color palettes for data visualization with ggplot2.
    The package includes custom themes for various plotting scenarios, and a collection
    of color palettes organized with a systematic naming scheme using the 'pal_' prefix 
    followed by the palette name and the number of colors available.
